-------------[ Itinerary 01 - The Cultural Odysseyt ]-------------
## **Day 01 – Arrival → Negombo (Coastal Welcome)**

**Route:** Airport → Negombo (20–30 mins)

* Airport pickup & warm welcome
* Transfer to hotel

**Afternoon:**

* Relax at **Negombo Beach**

**Meals:**

* Authentic Sri Lankan lunch

**Overnight:** Negombo beach hotel – Half Board

👉 *Why improved:* light recovery day after long international flight

---

## **Day 02 – Negombo → Anuradhapura (Ancient Kingdom Start)**

**Route:** Negombo → Anuradhapura (4–4.5 hrs)

**Afternoon Sacred City Tour:**

* **Sri Maha Bodhi**
* **Ruwanwelisaya**
* Jetavanaramaya
* Abhayagiri Dagoba
* Twin Ponds

**Overnight:** Anuradhapura lakefront hotel – Half Board

👉 *Why improved:* removes sightseeing pressure on arrival day, focuses full heritage immersion

---

## **Day 03 – Anuradhapura → Polonnaruwa (Ancient Civilizations Journey)**

**Route:** Anuradhapura → Polonnaruwa (2.5–3 hrs)

**Afternoon Exploration:**

* **Polonnaruwa Ancient City**
* Gal Vihara
* Parakrama Samudra

**Overnight:** Polonnaruwa hotel – Half Board

👉 *Why improved:* keeps Cultural Triangle progression logical and efficient

---

## **Day 04 – Polonnaruwa → Sigiriya → Dambulla (Cultural Triangle Core)**

**Morning:**

* Visit **Sigiriya Rock Fortress**

**Afternoon:**

* Visit **Dambulla Cave Temple**

**Optional Stop:**

* Nalanda Gedige

**Overnight:** Sigiriya / Dambulla hotel – Half Board

👉 *Why improved:* consolidates key UNESCO highlights into one efficient day

---

## **Day 05 – Sigiriya → Kandy (Cultural Capital Journey)**

**Route:** Sigiriya → Kandy (3 hrs)

**En-route Stop:**

* Nalanda Gedige (if not visited earlier)

**Kandy Highlights:**

* **Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic**
* **Kandy Lake**
* Cultural Dance Show

**Overnight:** Kandy hotel – Half Board

👉 *Why improved:* smooth transition from ancient heritage to cultural capital

---

## **Day 06 – Kandy (Hill Capital Exploration Day)**

* **Royal Botanic Gardens, Peradeniya**
* Kandy View Point
* Tea experience / spice garden visit

**Afternoon:**

* Transfer to Bentota (coastal drive 4–5 hrs)

**Evening:**

* Beach relaxation at **Bentota Beach**

**Overnight:** Bentota hotel – Half Board

👉 *Why improved:* adds proper beach transition instead of rushed travel

---

## **Day 07 – Bentota → Airport (Departure Day)**

**Route:** Bentota → Airport (2–2.5 hrs expressway)

**Morning:**

* Relax at beach / hotel leisure time

**Optional Stop (if time permits):**

* **Gangaramaya Temple**
* Colombo short city drive

**Lunch:** Colombo restaurant

**Transfer to airport for departure**



